HEADWORD: Conversance
<hw>Con"ver*sance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or
quality of being conversant; habit of familiarity; familiar
acquaintance; intimacy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
